race.description: Cmv Truck And Bus Warrnambool Handicap (Bm62)
race.comment: MY ZEPHYR (8) resumed in a 64 at Murray Bridge beaten a nose and brought strong Victorian provincial and metro form to that. She has performed second-up and is further improved. Can go one better on the 19-day return. FORAGOODCAUSE (5) has threatened her last two at Bendigo in stronger. Maps for a soft run and Yendall sticks aboard. Hits this at peak and is feared. MASKED MARAUDER (6) also presents fourth up and is better than the last two outings suggest. She resumed here with a narrow defeat and has the blinkers on for the first time. They may provide that extra spark and Meech replaces the apprentice. THE NARRATOR (3) creates interest resuming for the new yard. He's been freshened off a dominant all the way win in a Benalla Maiden, and the jumpouts leading into this have been sharp. Draws out but has to be kept very safe.
